                     <interp inst="t17770409-27-off137" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing a watch with one case made of silver, value 30 s. and a watch with an inside case made of base metal and an inside case of shagreen, value 30 s the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17770409-27-victim316" type="victimName">
                           William
                            Harrap
